item.title: Shine On, LG, Shine On
item.description:
Looking for a sleek and stylish device that’s more than just a pretty face? The LG Shine, available in vibrant red or classic black, is an engineering marvel that combines the functionality of a camera, media player, and cell phone all in one. Encased in attractive stainless steel, the LG Shine is a quad-band GSM phone compatible with AT&T’s 3G network. Its unique 2.2-inch mirror LCD provides a wide viewing angle and adds to its sleek appeal...
